<section id="hashmaps" class="scroll-mt-24 mb-32">
    <h1>HashMaps</h1>
    <p class="text-xl text-neutral-600 mb-10">
        HashMaps (or Dictionaries) are collections of key-value pairs, useful for storing structured data.
    </p>

    <h3>Basic Usage</h3>
    <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-600">Create maps using curly braces <code>{}</code> and access values using keys.</p>
    
    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-200 shadow-xl shadow-neutral-200/40 bg-white mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center h-10 px-4 bg-neutral-50 border-b border-neutral-200">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-300 border border-neutral-400/30"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-300 border border-neutral-400/30"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-300 border border-neutral-400/30"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mx-auto text-xs font-mono text-neutral-500 font-medium tracking-wide">map_create.jackal</div>
        </div>
        <pre class="!border-none !rounded-none !shadow-none !mb-0 !bg-white !text-neutral-800 p-6 text-[13.5px] leading-7"><code><span class="text-neutral-400 italic">// Create a map</span>
<span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">let</span> person = {<span class="text-green-600">"name"</span>: <span class="text-green-600">"Jack"</span>, <span class="text-green-600">"age"</span>: <span class="text-orange-600">5</span>};

<span class="text-neutral-400 italic">// Access a value by key</span>
<span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">print</span> person[<span class="text-green-600">"name"</span>]; <span class="text-neutral-400 italic">// Output: Jack</span></code></pre>
    </div>

    <h3>Modification</h3>
    <p class="mb-4 text-neutral-600">HashMaps are mutable. You can update existing keys or add new ones easily.</p>

    <div class="rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-neutral-200 shadow-xl shadow-neutral-200/40 bg-white mb-6">
        <div class="flex items-center h-10 px-4 bg-neutral-50 border-b border-neutral-200">
            <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-300 border border-neutral-400/30"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-300 border border-neutral-400/30"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-neutral-300 border border-neutral-400/30"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="mx-auto text-xs font-mono text-neutral-500 font-medium tracking-wide">map_modify.jackal</div>
        </div>
        <pre class="!border-none !rounded-none !shadow-none !mb-0 !bg-white !text-neutral-800 p-6 text-[13.5px] leading-7"><code><span class="text-neutral-400 italic">// Update existing value</span>
person[<span class="text-green-600">"age"</span>] = <span class="text-orange-600">6</span>;
<span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">print</span> person[<span class="text-green-600">"age"</span>]; <span class="text-neutral-400 italic">// Output: 6</span>

<span class="text-neutral-400 italic">// Add new key-value pair</span>
person[<span class="text-green-600">"color"</span>] = <span class="text-green-600">"Orange"</span>;
<span class="text-purple-600 font-bold">print</span> person[<span class="text-green-600">"color"</span>]; <span class="text-neutral-400 italic">// Output: Orange</span></code></pre>
    </div>
</section>